    • addMeasuredVariables

      int addMeasuredVariables(String name, String unit, Double period, int qmin, int qmax)
      Add Metadata for time series.
      Parameters:
      name - : The name of data we want to study.
      unit - : Unit of data we want to study.
      period - : Time between data.
      qmin - : minimum of quality
      qmax - : maximum of quality
      Returns:
